            </div>
            <div class="h-degree">
              <span class="degree-code">H38</span>
              <span class="degree-name">Full Hard</span>
              <div class="strength-bar"><div class="strength-fill h3-fill" data-width="100"></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- H4x -->
        <div class="content-card-inner h-sub-section reveal">
          <h3>H4x &mdash; Strain Hardened &amp; Lacquered or Painted</h3>
          <p>Products that are strain hardened and subsequently subjected to a paint bake or lacquer cure cycle. The thermal exposure during curing results in some partial annealing. The mechanical properties of H4x tempers are similar to those of the corresponding H2x tempers.</p>
        </div>

