      <!-- Section 5: T - Thermally Treated -->
      <div class="section-block reveal">
        <h2 class="section-heading"><span class="section-num">05</span> T &mdash; Thermally Treated</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">The T temper applies to products that have been heat treated to produce stable tempers other than F, O, or H. The T designation is used for <strong>heat-treatable alloys</strong> in the 2xxx, 6xxx, and 7xxx series. A numeral 1 through 10 follows the T to indicate the specific sequence of treatments.</p>

        <!-- Solution Heat Treatment SVG -->
        <div class="content-card-inner svg-showcase reveal">
